io.atomix.primitive.operation.PrimitiveOperation

  • Packages that use PrimitiveOperation 
    Package Description
    io.atomix.primitive.operation
    Provides classes and interfaces for defining distributed primitive operations.
    io.atomix.primitive.proxy
    Provides interfaces for operating on distributed primitive services.
    io.atomix.protocols.backup.protocol
    Provides classes and managing cluster communication in support of a primary-backup replication protocol.
    io.atomix.protocols.backup.proxy
    Provides a PartitionProxy implementation for primary-backup.
    io.atomix.protocols.raft.protocol
    Provides RaftRequest and RaftResponse implementations for all internal Raft protocol communication.
    io.atomix.protocols.raft.service
    Provides classes for managing Raft-based primitive services.
    io.atomix.protocols.raft.storage.log.entry
    Provides RaftLogEntry implementations used internally to replicate state changes, sessions, and configuration changes in the cluster.
